How to build a maven project?

steps file-->new--other--maven--maven project-->next
-->create simple project-->use default location-->
-->Group Id--Artifact ID--Finish.
Then update properties file if needed
<properties>
	<maven.compiler.target>17</maven.compiler.target>
	<maven.compiler.source>17</maven.compiler.source>
	</properties>
	
	What is pom.xml file?
	Configuration file for the project
		
	What is artifactId ?
	Project Name
	
	What is the groupId ?
	Package Name
	
